name: HEN Lifetime
description: This is the lifetime in real time since the Hic et Nunc website was born, from the domain registration on November 7, 2020 - 07:06:28 UTC. From left to right are the years, days, hours, minutes and seconds of life on our beloved platform. A small tribute to this awesome platform that offers incredible opportunities for so many artists!  Minted on May 18, 2020 (192 days of HEN's life) - Programmed in JavaScript
